text: Food wasn't bad. But the pricing is atrocious!!! 1 small piece of chicken, with veg, bagedil and a fried egg with rice at $10???? This is Midview, Not MBS... willl never come here to get "carrot" again

Enjoy my lunch greatly today. Only discover yesterday about this lovely place @ Midview Blk 18 coffee shop. A simple assam pedas with sardine fish since their assam fish sold out at 12 noon with stir fried sambal brinjal and nice crispy fried tempeh. Will be my regular stall now.
